<MemberDefinition

  labels = {["static"]}>
Check if <code>Root</code> follows a pattern Root(ext(LHS), ext(RHS)) where <code>ext</code> is the same for both LHS and RHS (i.e., both are sext or both are zext) and LHS and RHS can be folded into Root.

AllowExtMask define which form <code>ext</code> can take in this pattern.


:::info
If the pattern can match with both zext and sext, the returned <a href="/docs/api/structs/anonymous-namespace-riscvisellowering-cpp-/combineresult">CombineResult</a> will feature the zext result.
:::

</SectionUser>
